---
import StatusCharts from "./StatusCharts.astro";
import type { StatusPayload } from "../../lib/status";
import { formatUpdatedAt, relativeTime } from "../../lib/status";

interface Props {
  data: StatusPayload | null;
  error: string | null;
}

const { data, error } = Astro.props;

const updatedStatic = data ? formatUpdatedAt(data.updated_at) : null;
---

<section>
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-10">
    <p class="mb-2 font-mono text-xs tracking-widest text-poi-accent dark:text-poi-accent uppercase">
      Live System Metrics
    </p>
    <h1 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">Live Demo</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-poi-muted">
    </p>
    {data && (
      <p class="mt-2 font-mono text-xs text-zinc-400 dark:text-poi-muted/60">
        <span id="updated-static">{updatedStatic}</span>
        <span class="mx-1 opacity-40">·</span>
        <span id="updated-relative" data-ts={data.updated_at}>—</span>
      </p>
    )}
  </div>

  <!-- Error state -->
  {error && (
    <p class="mb-8 font-mono text-xs text-zinc-400 dark:text-poi-muted/50">
      <span class="mr-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-400 align-middle"></span>
      data unavailable
    </p>
  )}

  {!data && !error && (
    <p class="mb-8 font-mono text-xs text-zinc-400 dark:text-poi-muted/50">
      <span class="mr-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-zinc-400 align-middle"></span>
      no data yet
    </p>
  )}

  <!-- Charts -->
  {data && <StatusCharts payload={JSON.stringify(data)} />}

  <!-- Footer -->
  <div class="mt-12 border-t border-zinc-200 pt-6 dark:border-zinc-700/40">
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <h2 class="font-mono text-lg text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">How to Read This Page</h2>

    <div class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200/80 bg-zinc-50/80 p-4 dark:border-zinc-700/50 dark:bg-zinc-900/40">
        <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">1. Order Latency</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
          バー確定から注文送信までの時間差です。判断から実行までの反応速度を見ています。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200/80 bg-zinc-50/80 p-4 dark:border-zinc-700/50 dark:bg-zinc-900/40">
        <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">2. Session Activity</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
          直近12時間の open / close イベントの流れです。セッション全体の動き方を見ます。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200/80 bg-zinc-50/80 p-4 dark:border-zinc-700/50 dark:bg-zinc-900/40">
        <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">3. Activity Heatmap</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
          日付と時刻ごとのイベント密度です。どの時間帯に動きやすいかを見ます。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200/80 bg-zinc-50/80 p-4 dark:border-zinc-700/50 dark:bg-zinc-900/40">
        <h3 class="font-mono text-sm text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">4. Data Freshness</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
          元データの遅れ具合です。表示内容がどれだけ新しいかを確認できます。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
      <p>
        各チャートは個人で運用しているパイプラインのデータを反映しています。機密性のある値は除外し、5分の遅延を挟んで公開しています。
      </p>
      <p class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-400 dark:text-poi-muted/60">
        Active Mon–Fri · 00:00–17:00 UTC (09:00–02:00 JST)
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-3 gap-y-1 font-mono text-xs text-zinc-400 dark:text-poi-muted/60">
      <a
        href="/posts/live-demo/"
        class="text-light-accent dark:text-poi-accent hover:underline"
      >
        background article
      </a>
      <span class="opacity-40">&middot;</span>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/yktsnet/portfolio-astro"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-light-accent dark:text-poi-accent hover:underline"
      >
        source code
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>

<script>
  import { relativeTime } from "../../lib/status";

  function updateRelative() {
    const el = document.getElementById("updated-relative");
    if (!el) return;
    const ts = el.dataset.ts;
    if (!ts) return;
    el.textContent = relativeTime(ts);
  }

  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
    updateRelative();
    setInterval(updateRelative, 30_000);
  });
</script>
